plot: All American med student Sam has planned an intimate getaway surprise for his girlfriend Paige, until Sam's best friend, Paige's brother Anthony, invites himself and their three other best friends along. The carefree group of twenty-something's arrive at the remote, picturesque home of Sam's uncle, unaware they have walked into a trap. They will spend the night in a fight for their lives, where everyone's strength, stamina, and bonds will be tested. What would you do for love? Inspired by true events.   Written by  anonymous
title: The Anniversary at Shallow Creek
